item.title: How do i make my self admin on [z508]?
item.dc:creator: @m4ul_tw1nz m4ul tw1nz
item.description:
@m4ul_tw1nz wrote:

Go to : Build —> Data ----> Characters ----> Mainsave And do : Ctrl + F and search for “rights” u will see:

“rights:0” change the “0” to —> “2”

Good Luck!
